{"tid":2132432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實DQ 喺2016年已經有，當時陳浩天，中出羊子，陳國強，賴綺雯，梁天琦被選舉主任裁定提名無效","createTime":"2020-07-30T11:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T14:43:04.000Z","uid":5843,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2a84cbea2930e96462bd18aa5d1a97cc0115fe0b","tid":2132432,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T11:26:33.000Z","msg":"之後係立法會宣誓風波，第一次司法覆核為梁頌恆及游蕙禎，第二次為梁國雄、姚松炎、羅冠聰及劉小麗<br />\n<br />\n今次大規模DQ，希望大家認清情況，一国兩制下只可以效忠共產黨，將來只有統派或獨派，再沒有中間所謂踩紅線嘅空間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b1/Yau-WC_%26_Baggio_Leung_Chung-hang_oath-taking_controversy_20161012.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb1%2FYau-WC_%2526_Baggio_Leung_Chung-hang_oath-taking_controversy_20161012.jpg&h=bf50e5f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">圖片為2016年DQ梁游</span>"},{"pid":"5f4c63edc9fb0edcc70d91c37d187bc80f876efb","tid":2132432,"uid":54721,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T11:52:56.000Z","msg":"當日統派開心緊少左對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9469f9521c190eb90182cdead75336ea189b4741","tid":2132432,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f4c63edc9fb0edcc70d91c37d187bc80f876efb","tid":2132432,"uid":54721,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T11:52:56.000Z","msg":"當日統派開心緊少左對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T11:56:22.000Z","msg":"一係就做唔反抗嘅白鴿，一係就等DQ<br />\n冇人係孤島<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1797fdf13b0af935e7b24921f57aac1bb66ba782","tid":2132432,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f4c63edc9fb0edcc70d91c37d187bc80f876efb","tid":2132432,"uid":54721,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T11:52:56.000Z","msg":"當日統派開心緊少左對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.